
This module provides a DataBase Interface for Ferite  using the libdbi library.

To use this module you will need a version of libdbi >= 0.6.7
libdbi is availible from http://libdbi.sf.net

You will also need a libdbi-driver. 
The libdbi drivers are avaliable trough the libdbi-drivers project on sourceforge. 
http://libdbi-drivers.sf.net

There are currently drivers for MySQL, PostgreSQL, SQLite, mSQL, Oracle and Firebird/Interbase.

More are on the way.   

